{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775877155579,"sessionID":"ses_2857b7443ffedBYuiC1TYbZRRS","part":{"id":"prt_d7a86ea8c001pOrz3PjZqCfHXO","messageID":"msg_d7a851002001VpLpmda3wovRl4","sessionID":"ses_2857b7443ffedBYuiC1TYbZRRS","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-96fc4613e9c24b0abcb2b4c8bb44f3fb","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-025/tasks.md","content":"# AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型 |\n| Module | `cmd/cli` |\n| Language | Python |\n| Size | M |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: AgentMetadata Model (ST-1)\n\n- [x] **T1.1**: Implement `AgentMetadata` Pydantic BaseModel with all required fields\n  - Purpose: Define primary data model for agent configuration stored as YAML\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py:8-30`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_valid -v`\n\n- [x] **T1.2**: Implement `language` field validator\n  - Purpose: Validate language is one of ['python', 'java'] with lowercase normalization\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py:32-39`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_invalid_language -v`\n\n- [x] **T1.3**: Implement `build_mode` field validator\n  - Purpose: Validate build_mode is one of ['local', 'cloud'] with lowercase normalization\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py:41-48`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_invalid_build_mode -v`\n\n- [x] **T1.4**: Implement `port` field validator\n  - Purpose: Validate port is in range 1-65535\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py:50-55`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_invalid_port_low -v`\n\n### Phase 2: MetadataOptions Dataclass (ST-2)\n\n- [x] **T2.1**: Implement `MetadataOptions` dataclass with all CLI options fields\n  - Purpose: Define dataclass for mapping command-line arguments to metadata fields\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/models/pack_models.py:6-21`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.models.pack_models import MetadataOptions; print(MetadataOptions.__dataclass_fields__)\"`\n\n- [x] **T2.2**: Implement `MetadataOptions.from_options()` factory method\n  - Purpose: Create MetadataOptions from dict filtering None values\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/models/pack_models.py:23-26`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.models.pack_models import MetadataOptions; opt = MetadataOptions.from_options({'agent_name': 'test', 'port': 8080}); print(opt.agent_name)\"`\n\n### Phase 3: MetadataService Core Methods (ST-3)\n\n- [x] **T3.1**: Implement `MetadataService.__init__` with verbose flag\n  - Purpose: Initialize service with verbose flag for logging control\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py:59-60`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_load_agent_metadata_yaml -v`\n\n- [x] **T3.2**: Implement `load_metadata()` with fallback filename list\n  - Purpose: Load metadata from workspace, falling back through ['agent_metadata.yaml', 'agent.yaml', 'metadata.yaml']\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py:62-72`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_load_fallback_agent_yaml -v`\n\n- [x] **T3.3**: Implement `save_metadata()` with YAML serialization settings\n  - Purpose: Save metadata to agent_metadata.yaml with exclude_none, indent=2, no flow style\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py:74-79`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_save_excludes_none -v`\n\n- [ ] **T3.4**: Implement `update_metadata()` method\n  - Purpose: Load, apply updates dict, save, and return new AgentMetadata\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_update -v`\n\n- [ ] **T3.5**: Implement `validate_workspace()` method\n  - Purpose: Validate workspace structure and language-specific requirements\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_validate_workspace_python -v`\n\n- [ ] **T3.6**: Implement `_validate_python_workspace()` helper\n  - Purpose: Check for at least one *.py file in workspace root\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_validate_python_workspace_has_py -v`\n\n- [ ] **T3.7**: Implement `_validate_java_workspace()` helper\n  - Purpose: Check for pom.xml in workspace\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_validate_java_workspace_has_pom -v`\n\n### Phase 4: Comprehensive Unit Tests (ST-4)\n\n- [x] **T4.1**: Test AgentMetadata valid creation\n  - Purpose: Verify AgentMetadata creates with required fields and defaults\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:11-20`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_valid -v`\n\n- [x] **T4.2**: Test AgentMetadata invalid language rejection\n  - Purpose: Verify ValidationError for unsupported language\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:22-28`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_invalid_language -v`\n\n- [x] **T4.3**: Test AgentMetadata invalid build_mode rejection\n  - Purpose: Verify ValidationError for unsupported build_mode\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:30-37`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_invalid_build_mode -v`\n\n- [x] **T4.4**: Test AgentMetadata port range validation\n  - Purpose: Verify ValidationError for port outside 1-65535 range\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:39-72`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_invalid_port_high -v`\n\n- [x] **T4.5**: Test load_metadata from agent_metadata.yaml (primary)\n  - Purpose: Verify loading from primary filename\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:76-91`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_load_agent_metadata_yaml -v`\n\n- [x] **T4.6**: Test load_metadata fallback to agent.yaml\n  - Purpose: Verify fallback to second filename when primary missing\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:93-104`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_load_fallback_agent_yaml -v`\n\n- [x] **T4.7**: Test load_metadata fallback to metadata.yaml\n  - Purpose: Verify fallback to third filename when first two missing\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:106-118`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_load_fallback_metadata_yaml -v`\n\n- [x] **T4.8**: Test load_metadata FileNotFoundError when all missing\n  - Purpose: Verify FileNotFoundError raised when no metadata files exist\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:158-160`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_load_no_files -v`\n\n- [x] **T4.9**: Test save