tadata)\n                            ├── T3.3 (save_metadata)\n                            └── T3.4 (update_metadata)\n\nT3.2 + T3.3 ────────────────┬── T3.4 (update_metadata)\n                            ├── T3.5 (validate_workspace)\n                            ├── T3.6 (_validate_python_workspace)\n                            └── T3.7 (_validate_java_workspace)\n\nT3.5 ───────────────────────┬── T3.6 (_validate_python_workspace)\n                            └── T3.7 (_validate_java_workspace)\n\nT1.1-T3.7 ──────────────────┬── T4.1-T4.18 (comprehensive unit tests)\n                            └── T5.1-T5.8 (integration tests)\n\nT4.1-T4.18 ──────────────────┬── T5.1-T5.8 (integration tests)\n```\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n| Task | Verification Command |\n|------|----------------------|\n| T1.1 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_valid -v` |\n| T1.2 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_invalid_language -v` |\n| T1.3 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_invalid_build_mode -v` |\n| T1.4 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_invalid_port_low -v` |\n| T2.1 | `python -c \"from agentcube.models.pack_models import MetadataOptions; print('OK')\" |\n| T2.2 | `python -c \"from agentcube.models.pack_models import MetadataOptions; opt = MetadataOptions.from_options({'agent_name': 'test'}); print(opt.agent_name)\"` |\n| T3.1 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_load_agent_metadata_yaml -v` |\n| T3.2 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_load_fallback_agent_yaml -v` |\n| T3.3 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_save_excludes_none -v` |\n| T3.4 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestM