| Uses | - | Integration: InvokeRuntime reads metadata |\n| `cmd/cli/tests/test_status_runtime.py` | Uses | - | Integration: StatusRuntime loads metadata |\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n### Metadata File Fallback Priority\n\nThe `load_metadata()` method searches for metadata files in this order:\n1. `agent_metadata.yaml` (canonical, preferred)\n2. `agent.yaml` (fallback)\n3. `metadata.yaml` (fallback)\n\nThis allows backward compatibility with existing agent projects.\n\n### YAML Serialization Configuration\n\n```python\nyaml.dump(\n    metadata.model_dump(exclude_none=True),\n    f,\n    default_flow_style=False,  # Use block style, not flow style\n    indent=2,                   # 2-space indentation\n    sort_keys=False,            # Preserve field order from model\n)\n```\n\n### Language-Specific Workspace Validation\n\n| Language | Validation Requirement |\n|----------|----------------------|\n| python | At least one `*.py` file in workspace root |\n| java | `pom.xml` file must exist in workspace |\n\n### Error Handling Patterns\n\n```python\ntry:\n    with open(filepath, \"r\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n        data = yaml.safe_load(f) or {}\n    return AgentMetadata(**data)\nexcept yaml.YAMLError as e:\n    raise ValueError(f\"Invalid YAML in {filename}: {e}\")\nexcept ValidationError as e:\n    raise ValueError(f\"Schema validation failed: {e}\")\n```\n\n### Constants Reference\n\n```python\nMETADATA_FILENAMES = [\"agent_metadata.yaml\", \"agent.yaml\", \"metadata.yaml\"]\nCANONICAL_METADATA_FILENAME = \"agent_metadata.yaml\"\nSUPPORTED_LANGUAGES = [\"python\", \"java\"]\nSUPPORTED_BUILD_MODES = [\"local\", \"cloud\"]\nDEFAULT_PORT = 8080\n```\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Timeline\n\n| Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n|-------|-------|--------|------------|\n| Phase 1: AgentMetadata Model | T1.1-T1.4 | Done | 100% |\n| Phase 2: MetadataOptions | T2.1-T2.2 | Done | 100% |\n| Phase 3: MetadataService Core | T3.1-T3.3 | Done | 100% |\n| Phase 3: MetadataService Core | T3.4-T3.7 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 4: Comprehensive Tests | T4.1-T4.10 | Done | 100% |\n| Phase 4: Comprehensive Tests | T4.11-T4.18 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 5: Integration Tests | T5.1-T5.8 | Pending | 0% |\n\n**Total Progress: 46% Complete (13/28 tasks)**\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Design: `changes/AR-025/design.md`\n- cli-toolkit/design.md — CLI toolkit architecture\n- cli-toolkit/spec.md — CLI specification (workspace validation, metadata format)\n- AR-024 — DockerService pattern (similar task structure)"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/models/pack_models.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-025/tasks.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-025/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775877155553,"end":1775877155576}}}}
